snippet.title: Hot Heat Reset (Demo Gameplay)
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay video of "Hot Heat Reset" demo version. A maze action game where you play as an unknown speedster hiding under a skull who is in pursuit to recover his stolen lands where an explosives factory is under operation. Reset Everything! 

Developer: n3r4zzurr0
Publisher: n3r4zzurr0
Genre: Action, Indie, Puzzle
Release Date: April 2023
Reviewed on: PC/Windows
Available on: PC/Windows

You can find Hot Heat Reset here: 
🕹️Steam► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2197360/Hot_Heat_Reset/
